### 알림 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 개별 알림 읽기 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 알림 전체 읽음 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
